author: Tesla
description:
25MW / 900MWh of Megapack provides power in Chile’s Atacama Desert, considered the driest desert on earth. Megapacks for Colbun’s Celda Solar project were manufactured in our newest Megafactory in Shanghai, and will provide critical grid stability, supporting the high penetration of solar in the region.

title: Powering Chile's Renewable Future | Megapack
